<p>Why? Staff are community members and writers just like everybody. They just also have big reputations and quality writing skills. I don't follow your position that a group of community members actively working toward creating something that they enjoy is somehow crossing a line. Ressurection is not established lore. It is not the official canon.</p>
<p>The staff members are excited about this canon, so they are writing things for this canon. That does not mean that they are forcing the hand of the wiki or attemping to change the tone. It means that <em>the staff members are excited about this canon, so they are writing things for this canon.</em></p>
