														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2265515">
									

<p>I don't mean to be rude or to what, but I've been writing my unrelated vignette series separate and unrelated to Resurrection. I haven't noticed any kind of lack of attention to my tales or a dip in such. Old Kansas Sector's ratings hasn't really fluctuated dramatically with the introduction of Resurrection either (that can't be explained with like, that it's a series or that the most recent tales are relatively recent).</p>
<p>So if Resurrection is in fact drowning out other tales, am I just not seeing it?</p>

