																		Analysis of Audience Dilution Based on Tales Posted After Resurrection
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bryx" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1786305); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1786305&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610252598" alt="Bryx" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1786305)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bryx" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1786305); return false;" >Bryx</a></span> <span class="odate time_1428372602 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">07 Apr 2015 02:10</span>
